The 13th edition of the Nigerian Entertainment Awards (NEA) was held on Saturday, November 10th, 2018 at the University of the District of Columbia Theater of the Arts in Washington, DC. The award covers various sections of the entertainment industry, including, music, movies, disc jockeying, record executives, comedy and a category for artistes in the diaspora. Davido and Tiwa Savage were the big winners of the night taking home Afropop Male and Female Artists of the year respectively.
Below is the complete list of winners for the music categories at NEA 2018< Adekunle Gold Skepta Small Doctor
Teni
blazer Artist of the Year
Duncan Mighty
Freshvibes Artist of the Year
